ZH: 我的航班今天下午出发。
EN: My flight departs this afternoon.

ZH: 他的航班延误了两个小时。
EN: His flight was delayed for two hours.

ZH: 明天早上的航班取消了。
EN: Tomorrow morning's flight has been canceled.

ZH: 我们需要预订明年的航班。
EN: We need to book flights for next year.

ZH: 你知道今天的航班准点吗？
EN: Do you know if today's flight is on time?

ZH: 明天的航班预计会有风暴。
EN: Tomorrow's flight is expected to have a storm.

ZH: 我们必须提前打电话确认登机口和航班。
EN: We must call ahead to confirm the gate and flight.

ZH: 飞行员报告说航班会延误一段时间。
EN: The pilot reports that the flight will be delayed for some time.

ZH: 我已经为我们的航班订购了经济舱。
EN: I have booked economy class for our flight.

ZH: 请提前办理登机手续，以确保航班。
EN: Please check-in early to ensure your flight.

ZH: 航班已经起飞了，你得等下一班。
EN: The flight has already taken off, you will have to wait for the next one.

ZH: 因为天气原因，我们的航班被取消了。
EN: Our flight has been canceled due to weather conditions.

ZH: 我们的航班延误了，我们可能会错过下一班。
EN: Our flight is delayed, we may miss the next one.

ZH: 你在哪个航班上？我在航班847上。
EN: Which flight are you on? I am on flight 847.

ZH: 这是一架去往纽约的航班。
EN: This is a flight to New York.

ZH: 我们需要在前往机场的路上检查航班状态。
EN: We need to check the flight status on our way to the airport.

ZH: 我的航班预计会在晚上9点到达。
EN: My flight is expected to arrive at 9 pm.

ZH: 我们需要提前两个小时到达机场以办理登机手续和安检。
EN: We need to arrive at the airport two hours early for check-in and security.

ZH: 飞机已经在起飞之前检查了航班。
EN: The plane has checked the flight before takeoff.

ZH: 我们的航班号是CA987。
EN: Our flight number is CA987.
